title: Ted Lieu
deleted: Ted Lieu is the congressman who attempted to show that Candace Owens, a conservative, was a huge supporter of Hitler using a clip from an interview she did…only to have Ms. Owens reveal that the clip was doctored and expose Congressman Lieu as a fraud  {{short description|U.S. Representative from California}}

title: Ted Lieu
added: Ted Lieu attempted to discredit Candace Owens, an outspoken conservative, regarding her views on Hitler using clips from an interview where Candace was talking about Nationalism . Candace referred Congressman Lieu, and all those members of the committee and the C-Span listeners to the full audio tape. This interview shows that she called Hitler despicable and said he was NOT a nationalist, that nationalists don’t kill their own people. <ref>{{Cite web|title=User Clip: Candace Owens Full Response to Ted Lieu {{!}} C-SPAN.org|url=https://www.c-span.org/video/?c4791195/user-clip-candace-owens-full-response-ted-lieu|access-date=2021-09-10|website=www.c-span.org|language=en-us}}</ref>
